of Manischewitz Elderberry produced during

00:56:57.170 --> 00:57:03.599
the Johnson Administration that lasted us
at least until the ouster of Tricky Dick.

00:57:03.599 --> 00:57:08.690
In recalling it now, I know it was an old
bottle because its familiar clunky square

00:57:08.690 --> 00:57:12.249
shape did not have a government warning label
on it.

00:57:12.249 --> 00:57:17.220
“Though it was possible that the warning
had fallen off due to exposure to toxic levels

00:57:17.220 --> 00:57:22.519
of mutant microbial life forms germinating
in the science experiment that was my mother's

00:57:22.519 --> 00:57:29.180
refrigerator. My parents were quite moderate
in their consumption, considered it extremely

00:57:29.180 --> 00:57:35.150
bad form not to at least take a taste of wine
when the berakhah , or ritual blessing over

00:57:35.150 --> 00:57:37.480
the wine, was said.

00:57:37.480 --> 00:57:42.839
“I remember one Seder when it was absolutely
impossible for me to consider tasting this

00:57:42.839 --> 00:57:49.319
impossibly disgusting liquid semi-life form
that had been decanted and recanted an endless

00:57:49.319 --> 00:57:55.930
number of times. 'Just a taste, Alex. It wouldn't
kill you,' my mother says to me.

00:57:55.930 --> 00:58:02.220
“'No Mother, I beg to differ. It would kill
me. In fact, it will kill all of us. The CDC

00:58:02.220 --> 00:58:06.650
in Atlanta will be very interested to know
why the entire Trotanoy family of Newark,

00:58:06.650 --> 00:58:13.359
New Jersey, was sickened unto death by uncontrollable
hemorrhagic bleeding from all of their orifices,

00:58:13.359 --> 00:58:17.349
as well as from the formation of gangrenously
separating green pus.'

00:58:17.349 --> 00:58:22.990
“ 'Would you look at the mouth on him?'
she asks my father. 'He's such an expert wine

00:58:22.990 --> 00:58:28.380
taster. I don't know what kind of palate you
have Mr. Big Shot, Mr. Wine Snob, but you've

00:58:28.380 --> 00:58:33.480
got quite a mouth on you, I'll tell you that,
Alex.' 'Are you or are you not going to say

00:58:33.480 --> 00:58:35.759
a barakhah and taste the wine?'

00:58:35.759 --> 00:58:40.960
“'Please, Mother. I'd rather not.' 'Are
you saying that you're too good, too refined,

00:58:40.960 --> 00:58:44.599
too la-di-da for Manischewitz?' 'Uh, yes,
Mother, I am.'

00:58:44.599 --> 00:58:46.829
[laughter]

00:58:46.829 --> 00:58:53.180
'As your mother, I command you to taste the
wine.' This would be utterly comical except

00:58:53.180 --> 00:58:58.769
for the fact that my mother, and I'm not kidding,
Doctor, my mother had taken the corkscrew

00:58:58.769 --> 00:59:04.900
into her hand and was holding the business
end of it poised to my throat.' 'Just take

00:59:04.900 --> 00:59:10.700
one little sippy for your mother, Alex.' My
mother was going to stab me with a corkscrew

00:59:10.700 --> 00:59:14.279
if I did not take at least a little sippy
of Manischewitz." [audience laughs]

00:59:14.279 --> 00:59:15.279
[end of reading]

00:59:15.279 --> 00:59:16.279
There you have it.

